    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. 1, Colobothea sublunulata Zajciw Ƥ; 2, Colobothea lunulata Lucas Ƥ; 3, Colobothea naevigera Bates Ƥ; 4, Colobothea sordida Aurivillius Ƥ; 5, Colobothea bisignata Bates 3; 6, Colobothea brullei Gahan Ƥ." ;
