<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.294465>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. 13, Colobothea berkovi Monné & Monné, sp. nov. 3; 14, Colobothea assimilis Aurivillius 3; 15, Colobothea plagiata Aurivillius Ƥ; 16, Colobothea macularis (Olivier) Ƥ; 17, Colobothea rubroornata Zajciw 3; 18, Colobothea varia (Fabricius) 3." ;
